---
import BaseLayout from "../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---
<BaseLayout title="Documents">
  <h1>Documents</h1>

  <p>Documents are file uploads (PDFs, Word, etc.) with title, description, category, and optional members-only flag.</p>
  <h2>Categories</h2>
  <p>Configured via Site Settings → Content → DocumentCategoriesJson. Assign one category per document.</p>
  <h2>Storage</h2>
  <p>Files store in Azure Blob Storage. The container is private; downloads happen via signed URLs the API issues per request.</p>
</BaseLayout>
